<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }
        * {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25em;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        /* layout */
        .wrapper {
            min-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <h1 class="content">Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in ht video "<%= title %>".</p>
    <p>Please login to your website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
    <p>Thanks you for being a part of our community!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>